title: Middle Child Album Art
body:
![alt text](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/cW9wh2KwK_q-tNlm_6U84FbssnZlwb-sHmLb2YeBvLnVTREUrmplnO9tt1qTjtUscy_Ivcoxmxo=s180-c-e100-rwu-v1 "Middle Child JCole Album Art")

A recreation of the album cover for J.Cole's recent single 'Middle Child'. This lab will hopefully be the first of a series of interactive experiences I make for the music I'm listening to.
